            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>暴雪娱乐制作的经典 MMORPG《World of Warcraft》（WoW）今年迎接 20 周年之际，提起，就不得不提丹麦著名电竞配件制造商 SteelSeries 。过往 SteelSeries 推出了不少电竞产品，今次就推出了一系列电竞用品庆祝 WoW 20 周年。最近 Unwire 编辑部就收到来自 SteelSeries 的 Arctis Nova 7 Wireless 电竞耳机、Aerox 9 Wireless 无线电竞滑鼠，以及 QcK 电竞滑鼠垫，全部均为 WoW 20 周年纪念款。现在就让小编和大家开箱看看这几款精美的电竞产品吧。</p><h2>SteelSeries Arctis Nova 7 Wireless 无线电竞耳机</h2><p>今次 SteelSeries 推出了兼容性高的 Arctis Nova 7 Wireless，特设 Dongle，不论是 PC、PlayStation、Switch、Mac 的用家都可享受到电竞快感，更有快速切换无线耳机功能，只需一键即可切换 2.4GHz 或蓝牙。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00970-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00970-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00970.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲SteelSeries Arctis Nova 7 Wireless</p><p>打开包装后，除了耳机本体外，内里附上了一张 WoW  Grinning Reaver mount 兑换券、一条 USB-C 转 USB-A 接收器延长线、一条 USB-C 转 USB-A 线、一条 3.5mm 线，以及一个接收器。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268578" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01014-1-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01014-1-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01014-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲USB-C 转 USB-A 接收器延长线、 USB-C 转 USB-A 线、 3.5mm 线以及接收器</p><h2>上手有份量　耳垫舒适</h2><p>与一般 SteelSeries 的黑色为主不同，SteelSeries Arctis Nova 7 Wireless 这次特地采用了黑金配色，彰显其 World of Warcraft 20 周年纪念版身份。小编开箱上手后觉得耳机非常扎实，头带位置采用金属材质，其余如耳筒部分则使用塑胶。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268603" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00974-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00974-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00974.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>头带部份可以拆除及移动，耳罩用上了可更换的透气布网及 AirWeave 记忆棉耳垫，实戴一阵亦不觉局促，记忆棉耳垫亦非常舒适，不易移位。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268604" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00983-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00983-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00983.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可轻松徒手拆除头带，以便调整至最舒适位置</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00985-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00985-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00985.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲耳罩厚实，佩戴舒适</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/arctis-nova-5-wireless/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Steelseries Arctis Nova 5 Wireless 耳机　60 小时长续航力 + 一键切换 2.4GHz 与蓝牙 + 兼容性高</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2><strong>实体按键</strong><strong>丰富</strong><strong>　方便玩家快速操作</strong></h2><p>Arctis Nova 7 Wireless 耳罩两边均设有不同实体按键，让用家可以在耳机上调节大部份控制。Nova 7 Wireless 左边设一拨轮用于控制音量，另外亦配备静音键；右边有开关及蓝牙按键、ChatMix 控制盘及 USB-C 充电插孔，操作上与大部份 Steelseries 耳机类似。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00978-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00978-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00978.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02052-694x463.avif 694w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02052-scaled.avif 1280w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />▲左边有音量控制拨轮及静音键</picture></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268607" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00979-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00979-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00979.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02051-694x463.avif 694w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02051-scaled.avif 1280w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture>▲右边有开关及蓝牙按键、ChatMix 控制盘及 USB-C 充电插孔</picture></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268608" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00976-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00976-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00976.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture>▲</picture>伸缩式 ClearCast 咪高峰（开启）</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268609" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00977-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00977-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00977.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02051-694x463.avif 694w,https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/dsc02051-scaled.avif 1280w" type="image/avif" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></picture></p><p style="text-align: center;"><picture>▲不使用时可收纳回耳罩内</picture></p><h2>Aerox 9 Wireless 无线电竞滑鼠</h2><p>SteelSeries Aerox 9 Wireless 左侧列出了 12 个数字键，可任由玩家自定义，大大增加可塑性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00986-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00986-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00986.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268571" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00993-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00993-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00993.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲内附 USB-C 线、PTFE 滑鼠脚垫、WoW  Lil&#8217; Flameo 兑换券</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00989-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00989-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00989.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲WoW 「W」字标记</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00987-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00987-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00987.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>如果你是 WoW 老玩家，相信会几欣赏这列快捷键，但如果你之前没有用过同类型滑鼠，要学习用大拇指精准控制这 12 个数字键，需要一定时间，因按键非常密集且紧凑，要用一定时间熟习惯控制。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268572" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00994-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00994-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00994.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲旁边有 12 个快捷键，可由玩家自定义</p><h2>QcK XXL 滑鼠垫（90cm x 40 cm）</h2><p>滑鼠垫上印有改变 Azeroth 历史的 The Sword of Sargeras，玩家可以用这款 XXL 尺寸的微编织布滑鼠垫装饰办公桌。要留意这款滑鼠垫尺寸颇大，长阔为 900 x 400 mm。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268573" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00995-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00995-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00995.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268574" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00997-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00997-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan00997.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268575" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01010-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01010-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01010.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268576" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01008-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01008-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/kan01008.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲滑鼠垫颇大，可容纳键盘连滑鼠</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/27/arctis-nova-5-wireless/mobile-music/headphones/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Steelseries Arctis Nova 5 Wireless 耳机　60 小时长续航力 + 一键切换 2.4GHz 与蓝牙 + 兼容性高</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/10/steelseries-world-of-warcraft/game-channel/">【开箱】SteelSeries x Warcraft 20 周年　Arctis Nova 7 无线耳机 + Aerox 9 无线滑鼠 + QcK 电竞滑鼠垫</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
