        </item>
        <item>
            <title>任天堂推智能音乐闹钟 Alarmo　可爱游戏主题可透过动作感应互动</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/10/nintendo-alarmo/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nintendo-alarmo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/10/10/nintendo-alarmo/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 10 Oct 2024 06:00:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Alarmo]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[任天堂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[闹钟]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1268382</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>任天堂除了游戏机之外，间中也会推出一些有趣的周边商品，最近他们就推出一款智能闹钟「Nintendo Sound Clock Alarmo」，除了有经典游戏角色主题和音效外，闹钟功能本身也很实用。<br /><span id="more-1268382"></span></p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_11920"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GQimR_GFNgo?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>Alarmo 的设计简单，前面设有彩色萤幕（并非触控萤幕），顶部设有可以着灯的旋钮和一些按键，用家可以选择自己喜欢的游戏主题，最初会有「超级玛利欧奥德赛」、「萨尔达传说，旷野之息」、「斯普拉遁 3」、「皮克敏 4」和「健身环大冒险」五款游戏主题可以选择，除了时间字型变化和画面人物会有不同，音效也会是游戏中的音乐。未来还会免费加入「集合啦！动物森友会」和「玛利欧赛车 8 豪华版」主题供下载。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268437" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fb12f1ed2edd47de1fe7-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fb12f1ed2edd47de1fe7-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/fb12f1ed2edd47de1fe7.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268438" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e331a5ae6ea54dab1c40-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e331a5ae6ea54dab1c40-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e331a5ae6ea54dab1c40.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268439" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/edcbc6fe1f3ff8568372-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/edcbc6fe1f3ff8568372-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/edcbc6fe1f3ff8568372.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268440" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/9692b3b3f3b77e2ec2e5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/9692b3b3f3b77e2ec2e5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/9692b3b3f3b77e2ec2e5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268441" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e33104d6b7ff1f5c33ed-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e33104d6b7ff1f5c33ed-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/e33104d6b7ff1f5c33ed.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>除了基本的闹钟功能外，Alarmo 还内置了动作感应器，用家移动身体时会有互动功能，例如，当使用者翻身时会播放金币音效，离开床铺时则会有激励的声音，令起床变成游戏般的体验。而如果闹钟响起后 20 分钟内使用者仍未起床，闹钟声音会变得更加大声。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268425" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/shot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/shot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/shot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>此外闹钟还内置睡眠记录和睡眠促进音效等其他功能，虽然并不是专业级分析，但仍然有一定的参考价值。而虽然闹钟有网络连线功能，不过并未与手机 App 连动，无法将睡眠数据输入手机，有点可惜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/alarmo44screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/alarmo44screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/alarmo44screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Alarmo 现于官方网上商店「My Nintendo Store」上向 Nintendo Switch Online 会员限定贩售，也会在「Nintendo TOKYO／OSAKA／KYOTO」等官方实体店铺开始销售，售价为 12,980 日元，而明年 2 月中开始会在全球发售，有兴趣的朋友可以留意了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268442" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/c9664bbc5c6de227a3d0-694x446.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/c9664bbc5c6de227a3d0-694x446.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/c9664bbc5c6de227a3d0.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1268443" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/af35d3583e42765776f4-694x446.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="446" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/af35d3583e42765776f4-694x446.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/af35d3583e42765776f4.jpeg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.nintendo.com/jp/hardware/alarmo/index.html">任天堂</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/08/15/nintendo-switch-2-rumors/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">任天堂 Switch 2 上市时间，传最快明年 4 月推出</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/19/nintendo-switch-official-joy-con-charging-stand/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">任天堂 Switch 上市 7 年半，原厂 Joy-Con 充电座终于推出</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/10/10/nintendo-alarmo/life-tech/">任天堂推智能音乐闹钟 Alarmo　可爱游戏主题可透过动作感应互动</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
